verbose_text: Since IFNbeta induced apoptosis of TE671 cells, vector control and NS5 expressing cells were used for test their susceptibility to IFNbeta, then treated singly or with both 10 mug/mL CsA (calcineurin inhibitor) and 1000 U/mL IFNbeta for 48 h. IFNbeta induced cytopathic effect of both cell types was photographed by light microscopy.
